    • Constructor Detail

      • Being

        public Being(MiddleEarthNode theParent,
             String name,
             String description)
        Constructs non-root nodes, setting the name and description.
        If theParent != null, tt "attaches" the object to its parent (and the parent to its child).
        Creation should be done by a factory/generator.
        Parameters:
        theParent - the parent node
        name - the name of this Being
        description - the description associate with this Being
